//Bodies I am passionate about mobile development and bring value to people"'"s lives through innovative mobile apps that build a more accessible, fair, creative society with unlimited opportunities for everyone.
I had the opportunity to complete my internship in the Holvi "'"s mobile development team, a digital bank oriented to entrepreneurs and small business owners. It is a FinTech company with headquarters in Finland and offices in Madrid and Berlin. There, I learned and worked as an Android developer with an expert team applying Scrum methodology. \n During this time, I have been implementing new features for Holvi "'"s Android native app such as a QR code scanner and bar codes for invoices, as well as other design, development, testing, optimization and support tasks.
I am currently working as an Android developer at TalentoMobile, a technology consulting company with different interesting projects in Madrid. So far I have been working on projects focused on the health sector, telecommunications and insurance companies.
My graduation project has consisted of the development of an educational native Android app written in Kotlin and Java for the management of banking services and expense control that allows the user to learn how to manage their savings. For the backend of my app I used the authentication and storage services of Google Firebase.
During my free time I am learning and developing my own projects with iOS and Swift because I love this platform and I want to become an expert on it.
